data.description: Welcome to this timeless gem, a 2-story, 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom historical home built in 1907, nestled on a generous 1.65-acre lot. Steeped in charm, it beautifully marries the elegance of the past with modern updates. With its well-preserved details and spacious interior, it's a unique opportunity to own a piece of history.   Recently painted exterior and updated kitchen which includes butcher block counter tops.  The three bathrooms in the home have also been updated and ready for new owners.   Book your viewing today and step into the grandeur of this 1907 classic.
